---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ProfileImage from "../assets/profile.png";
---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="min-h-svh grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] bg-[var(--bg-main)] overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="hero-right bg-[var(--bg-alt)] relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 lg:p-16 bg-dotted order-1 lg:order-2 overflow-hidden w-full min-h-[420px]">

    <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 w-44 p-4 rotate-3 bg-[var(--sticky-yellow)] shadow-lg border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      shipping hulak.app 📫<br />
      in dev as of<br />
      Mar '26
    </div>

    <div class="absolute top-[45%] right-6 w-44 p-4 -rotate-2 bg-[var(--sticky-red)] shadow-lg border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      TMKOC randomizer<br />
      yes it was<br />
      necessary
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 w-48 p-4 -rotate-2 bg-[var(--sticky-blue)] shadow-lg border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      KU · CS · 2025–2029<br />
      📚 studying & building
    </div>

    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-20 left-10 w-40 p-4 rotate-[8deg] bg-[var(--sticky-blue)] shadow-md border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      "to be or not to be"<br />
      just deploy bro
    </div>

    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-24 right-10 w-40 p-4 rotate-6 bg-[var(--sticky-red)] shadow-md border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      why is this not working<br />
      it worked 2 mins ago 💀
    </div>

    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-[65%] left-10 w-40 p-4 -rotate-4 bg-[var(--sticky-yellow)] shadow-md border border-[var(--border-light)] font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
      deploy → panic → fix → repeat
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-56 h-56 mb-6 transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2 z-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-[var(--text-main)] translate-x-1.5 translate-y-1.5"></div>
      <div class="absolute -inset-1 rounded-full border-4 border-[var(--accent)]"></div>
      <Image
        src={ProfileImage}
        alt="Rupak Chaulagain"
        class="relative w-56 h-56 rounded-full object-cover z-10 sepia-[0.1] saturate-90 shadow-xl"
      />
    </div>

    <p class="font-mono text-[0.6rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-faint)] text-center mb-4 z-10">
      fig. 1 — the developer in his natural state
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2 z-10">
      <div class="text-center border border-[var(--border-light)] p-3 bg-[var(--bg-main)] shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
        <span class="block font-serif text-[var(--accent)] text-2xl font-bold">6+</span>
        <span class="block font-mono text-[0.55rem] uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--text-faint)]">Projects</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center border border-[var(--border-light)] p-3 bg-[var(--bg-main)] shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
        <span class="block font-serif text-[var(--accent)] text-2xl font-bold">3+</span>
        <span class="block font-mono text-[0.55rem] uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--text-faint)]">Live apps</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center border border-[var(--border-light)] p-3 bg-[var(--bg-main)] shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2">
        <span class="block font-serif text-[var(--accent)] text-2xl font-bold">2029</span>
        <span class="block font-mono text-[0.55rem] uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--text-faint)]">Grad year</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="hero-left flex flex-col justify-center p-6 lg:p-16 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-[var(--border-light)] order-2 lg:order-1">

    <div class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--text-faint)] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 before:content-['>>>'] before:text-[var(--accent)] before:font-semibold">
      Student developer & builder
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-serif font-black text-5xl lg:text-8xl leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-2">
      Rupak
      <span class="italic text-[var(--accent)] font-normal block">Chaulagain</span>
    </h1>

    <blockquote class="italic text-lg mb-8 mt-6 border-l-4 border-[var(--accent)] pl-4 font-serif text-[var(--text-mid)] max-w-sm leading-snug">
      Making stuff, breaking stuff, and occasionally
      shipping stuff that people actually use.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 mb-8 font-mono text-sm">
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)] min-w-[80px]">Location</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--text-mid)]">Thimi, Bhaktapur, Nepal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)] min-w-[80px]">Current</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--text-mid)]">BSc CS @ Kathmandu University</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)] min-w-[80px]">Stack</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">Python · TS · Astro · FastAPI</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)] min-w-[80px]">Status</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">● open to opportunities</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="#projects" class="px-5 py-2 xl:px-8 xl:py-4 font-mono text-sm xl:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white bg-[var(--accent)] border-2 border-[var(--accent)] transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-[var(--text-main)] hover:border-[var(--text-main)]">
        See my work
      </a>
      <a href="#contact" class="px-5 py-2 xl:px-8 xl:py-4 font-mono text-sm xl:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-main)] border-2 border-[var(--text-mid)] transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-[var(--text-main)] hover:text-[var(--bg-main)]">
        Say hello
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/chaulagainrupak" target="_blank" class="px-5 py-2 xl:px-8 xl:py-4 font-mono text-sm xl:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-main)] border-2 border-[var(--text-mid)] transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.06] hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-[var(--text-main)] hover:text-[var(--bg-main)]">
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>